name: Karen Gillan
description:
Karen Sheila Gillan (born 28 November 1987) is a Scottish actress. She gained recognition for her work in British film and television, particularly for playing Amy Pond, a primary companion to the Eleventh Doctor in the science fiction series Doctor Who (2010–2013), for which she received several awards and nominations.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey, people of Civitai! I was off for a some days but here I am! Today I have a textual inversion of the lovely Karen Gillan! Hope you'll like her ;) I used 30 public images of her with a 6700 steps process. To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add kargillan87 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20/25, and CFG between 7 and 8 to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision;
